The -50 MR check is part of the chant's coding.<br>
The DoT crit AA is separate don't confuse the issue.<br>
Yes 8% is the chance to do a crit/tick (with level 3).<br>
So effectively 8% of the time you get the damage of another dot (for 1 tick)<br>
Its not spectacular but if you kite a lot and you've bough all the other AAs you want its more icing for the cake.<br>
<br>
Nothing in this expansion will dramaticaly redefine bards or their roles and I still think the cost/benefit ratio for these AAs is too high. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
